{"tid":1468441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公投 機場運動再設Deadline","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T04:14:15.000Z","uid":65981,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1721126b080e362f57541a09926e088d8395b6bc","tid":1468441,"uid":65981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:40:50.000Z","msg":"依兩日林鄭既回應擺明佢對我地癱瘓機場既做法束手無策，唯有出經濟同感情牌，將矛頭帶返落示威者度，造成民眾對立，<br />\n<br />\n所以我建議民宣／民間記者會可以再發起deadline，通知唔同國家既航空公司，喺九月一日前政府再無回應，將會無限期佔領機場，叫佢地慎重考慮取消九月之後既航班，咁樣既可以避免有外國旅客滯留香港既情況，同時避免流失民意。<br />\n<br />\n之前有連登巴絲發起咗籌款，好似有1m usd，有無相關既巴絲知道詳情，可唔可以喺各國報紙頭版登廣告，正式宣佈香港機場癱瘓行動？"},{"pid":"9786b5215435feadc0832778d8206d20573eaf82","tid":1468441,"uid":117550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:41:26.000Z","msg":"(突發)航空公司   民航處  機管局講大話<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468306</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8afe40f8df17a1d27d7c1f12cb3e498f711b06ad","tid":1468441,"uid":65981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:43:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5eb63c599d7e5fd3f0b0f06b60e04cdfdad06de9","tid":1468441,"uid":65981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:44:47.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"5a782b190ccffd0e9dc2ba12f832eafa795342e5","tid":1468441,"uid":65981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:44:57.000Z","msg":"十"},{"pid":"d548b5b7f41e6c096ad4c99ea37357a1645936b1","tid":1468441,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9786b5215435feadc0832778d8206d20573eaf82","tid":1468441,"uid":117550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:41:26.000Z","msg":"(突發)航空公司   民航處  機管局講大話<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468306</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:45:10.000Z","msg":"【訓撚醒未呀】港共政府 無辦法係機場清場 但 可以 連登分化粉碎呢個活動<br />\n<a href=\"h